data.description: ASSUMABLE VA LOAN!  You do not have to be a veteran to assume!  Finish this mortgage at 3.25% instead of the much higher rates of today! Move in ready home right in town! Home has been completely updated.  Enter home into the spacious great room. Master bedroom is split from the other 3 bedrooms. Granite counters in kitchen and bathrooms. Kitchen also has a large island with a wood countertop.  Vinyl flooring in all traffic areas, tile in bathrooms and carpet in bedrooms. Buyer/Buyer's Agent to verify all facts and figures.
